name: Predictability
description: Enabling reliable assumptions by individuals owners and operators about data and their processing.

name: Manageability
description: Providing the capability for granular administration of data.

name: Disassociability
description: Enabling the processing of data or events without association to individuals or devices.

name: Confidentiality
description: Preserving authorized restrictions on information access and disclosure.

name: Integrity
description: Guarding against improper information modification or destruction.

name: Availability
description: Ensuring timely and reliable access to and use of information.
